title: Did the trump test rates in Oklahoma have been 100% positive?
subtitle: An analysis of methyl data by MSNBC led to a misunderstanding.
author: Nur Ibrahim
vclaim: On June 20, 2020, the electoral gathering in Tulsa, Oklahoma, during the outbreak of the Corona virus epidemic, could have been linked to two days of positive COVID-19 tests of 100% reported in the state after more than a week.
